in the house to prove it.

1028
01:19:37.264 --> 01:19:40.232
-What did he leave?
-Well. he wouldn't say.

1029
01:19:41.343 --> 01:19:42.496
That business.

1030
01:19:42.520 --> 01:19:46.825
All them people around him
had him so paranoid.

1031
01:19:46.849 --> 01:19:48.991
